        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"22961\">Jai soni</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/101-design/topic/UI.20redesign.3A.20Use.20same.20.40.20symbol.20everywhere.20.2322816/near/1429599\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>just mentioning --&gt; <br>\n<span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"19257\">Alya Abbott</span>  we do have 1 more <code>@</code> here in the tooltip of this <code>@all</code> -&gt; do we want to change this too ?</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c9/JKeOoZtoLFKe1Vt930UfiBbV/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I think we can keep the plain text <code>@</code> there? But I'll defer to <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"22433\">@Vlad Korobov</span> .</p>",
        "id": 1429698,
